    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/d1f1d38ebdbfd335354b245129692927.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><strong>你</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改变地形现在是你的主要武器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改变单位也非常有用</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你不是将军——你是神。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需向部队下达命令——你可以直接改变大地：抬起山脉，淹没峡谷，随心所欲地重塑战场。因为你可以。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉传统命令吧——在这里，你的神力将决定战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全可预测的战斗——没有随机性，一切尽在掌控。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >间接控制单位——单位根据固定路径规则自主移动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控战场——你的能力允许你改变地形，甚至改变单位职业。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue-lite 重玩性——每次游戏构建独特法术和单位组合，解锁不同风格的新英雄。<br>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/22260a1a21333109e43fd53967636f56.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>变</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/a26f72b83847378b8b3a9ebcbcf62de2.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/5e3eb35ddb3eb0c649e84d40c01a9a84.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/5e3eb35ddb3eb0c649e84d40c01a9a84.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/5e3eb35ddb3eb0c649e84d40c01a9a84.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/cc37c8300784dc014697deefff0f636b.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/cc37c8300784dc014697deefff0f636b.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/cc37c8300784dc014697deefff0f636b.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
